  "detailed_description": "———————————————————————————————— <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1512830/extras/d6e63047719b0f3f7c9e966385ac419f.avif?t=1701754969\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1512830/extras/7533a56d0653881a95f3a5fafd3b56ad.avif?t=1701754969\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Discord：ysDzgVjRS3<br><br>  主角和她的妹妹俩人刚踏入社畜的世界，除了打工赚钱以外，<br>  她还得时刻注意，乡下小镇糟糕的治安带来的各种危险，<br>  当然，更多的危险来源自于主角她自己…… <br>———————————————————————————————— <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1512830/extras/3744811a7b5e9efcff47e6db0784d587.avif?t=1701754969\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1512830/extras/ab7801c06aa0c84dfbebe970341d2033.avif?t=1701754969\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1512830/extras/198b103afd3203275495e9ba880a8384.avif?t=1701754969\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>———————————————————————————————— <br><br>本作基于《OZ大乱斗NS》与《劳资的长假》系列的世界观，讲述了长假系列中登场的黑巢姐妹长大后的故事，<br>大幅改变了画风以外，也加入了换装系统等其他的要素，<br>时装里的每一个零件都可以更换，而且在不同角色穿着时都会以自己不同风格显示.<br>玩过系列其他作品的玩家一定会有不同的新体验.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1512830/extras/ea708353cb4140e296d8a508c56fd993.avif?t=1701754969\" width=592 height=672 /></span><br>————————————————————————————————",
